violations.description: Ensure the contrast between foreground and background colors meets WCAG 2 AA minimum contrast ratio thresholds

nodes.failureSummary:

  Element has insufficient color contrast of 4.03 (foreground color: #0085ca, background color: #ffffff, font size: 12.0pt (16px), font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1
